        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The &amp;quot;Saraswati Sadhana Yojana to Economically Backward Class Girls studying in Class 9&amp;quot;  is a welfare scheme by the Social Justice and Empowerment Department of Gujarat. The scheme offers free bicycles to girls enrolled in Class 9 in government and grant-in-aided schools, facilitating easier access to education and encouraging regular school attendance. This physical aid helps in improving educational participation and empowering female students from economically weaker backgrounds.\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n  - Free bicycle provided to each eligible girl student.\n\n<br>\n\n<br>\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "Under this scheme, free bicycle assistance is provided to economically backward class girls studying in Class 9 in government and grant-in-aid schools across Gujarat.\n\n",
        "exclusions_md": "<br>\n\n",
        "detailedDescription": [
          {
            "type": "align_justify",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "The \"Saraswati Sadhana Yojana to Economically Backward Class Girls studying in Class 9\"  is a welfare scheme by the Social Justice and Empowerment Department of Gujarat. The scheme offers free bicycles to girls enrolled in Class 9 in government and grant-in-aided schools, facilitating easier access to education and encouraging regular school attendance. This physical aid helps in improving educational participation and empowering female students from economically weaker backgrounds."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
