          "process_md": "> **Registration Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the official website: [www.digitalgujarat.gov.in](https://www.digitalgujarat.gov.in/)\n**Step 2:** Click on the “Register” button on the homepage.\n**Step 3:** You will be redirected to the registration form page.\n**Step 4:** Fill in the required details such as: Name, Email ID, Mobile Number, Password, etc.\n**Step 5:** Submit the registration form to create your account.\n> **Log In Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Go to [www.digitalgujarat.gov.in](https://www.digitalgujarat.gov.in/)\n**Step 2:** Click on the “Login” button.\n**Step 3:** Select the suitable login option (e.g., Citizen Login).\n**Step 4:** You will be redirected to the login form page.\n**Step 5:** Enter your registered Email ID/Mobile Number and Password.\n**Step 6:** Click Login to access your account.\n> **Apply for a New Service:**\n\n**Step 1:** Log in to the portal using your registered credentials.\n**Step 2:** After login, your user profile will appear showing all previously taken services.\n**Step 3:** Click on “Request a New Service” or the relevant option.\n**Step 4:** You will be redirected to a list of services.\n**Step 5:** Select the desired service from the list.\n**Step 6:** Click “Continue to Service”.\n**Step 7:** A form will open—fill in all the required information.\n**Step 8:** (Optional) Click to auto-fill details from your profile.\n**Step 9:** Click “Next” after completing each section.\n**Step 10:** Upload/attach the necessary documents or import them via DigiLocker.\n**Step 11:** Review all information and click “Submit” to complete the application.\n> **Contact Us:** [Click here.](https://www.digitalgujarat.gov.in/SchemPortal/ContactUs.aspx)\n\n"
        }
